metadata.name: Ashby
metadata.description: This is my life. This is what I do. GCSW. This is real footage that I filmed of the Ashby, Minnesota, EF4 tornado that occurred on July 8th of 2020. It was a life altering experience for me. Never have I felt such an adrenaline rush. Never have I been more alive. This is where I was meant to be.
